data.name: textBox3.Text
data.value:
Here you can Select additional File/Folder context menu entries. For example you will find easier to deal with Invalid or corrupted files if they are impossible to delete/rename (using Delete Inavlid Files option). The "Delete Long Path" will help you to delete very long path'es. Instant Share will add and option menu to the folders that allow you to instant share any folder in the network. Default permissions will allow to access it over nework as any user or (GUEST). Without any additional configuration or deal with permissions. For security reasons the default permissions only allows to access data, but does not allow to modify it. Take ownership option will allow you to reset or re-take files/folders NTFS permissions without any problems.
Have a nice using!

data.value:
Automata is a small tool for Microsoft Windows Operating System. It will help in various situations making easier to do most of windows system management from one window. This is early development version so don't expect anything in advanced level..
Feel free to drop an feature request or report a bug!
